---
---

<section id="sobre" class="py-24 bg-dark-900">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="mb-16 animate-slide-up">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-dark-50">Sobre Mí</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-accent-primary rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
      <!-- Descripción -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
        <p class="text-dark-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Soy un desarrollador apasionado por crear experiencias digitales hermosas y funcionales. Con experiencia en tecnologías web modernas, me especializo en construir aplicaciones que combinan diseño elegante con funcionalidad robusta.
        </p>
        <p class="text-dark-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Mi enfoque es simple: comprender el problema, diseñar la solución y ejecutarla con precisión  dejando siempre código limpio y mantenible.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Números/Stats -->
      <div class="space-y-4 animate-scale-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-700 p-6 rounded-xl hover:border-accent-primary/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-primary mb-2">50+</div>
          <div class="text-dark-400 text-sm">Proyectos</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-700 p-6 rounded-xl hover:border-accent-primary/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-secondary mb-2">30+</div>
          <div class="text-dark-400 text-sm">Clientes</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-800 border border-dark-700 p-6 rounded-xl hover:border-accent-primary/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-primary mb-2">5+</div>
          <div class="text-dark-400 text-sm">Años</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Info items -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-16">
      <div class="group p-6 bg-dark-800 rounded-xl border border-dark-700 hover:border-accent-primary/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-dark-800/50 cursor-pointer animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-accent-primary/20 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark-50 mb-2">Desarrollo</h3>
        <p class="text-dark-400 text-sm">Full Stack con tecnologías modernas</p>
      </div>

      <div class="group p-6 bg-dark-800 rounded-xl border border-dark-700 hover:border-accent-primary/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-dark-800/50 cursor-pointer animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-accent-primary/20 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark-50 mb-2">Diseño</h3>
        <p class="text-dark-400 text-sm">UI/UX enfocado en experiencia</p>
      </div>

      <div class="group p-6 bg-dark-800 rounded-xl border border-dark-700 hover:border-accent-primary/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-dark-800/50 cursor-pointer animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-accent-primary/20 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark-50 mb-2">Innovación</h3>
        <p class="text-dark-400 text-sm">Soluciones creativas</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
